For An Act To Be Entitled
10
11 AN ACT TO AMEND THE REVISED ARKANSAS ANATOMICAL GIFT
12 ACT; TO ALLOW CERTAIN CLASSES OF PERSONS TO REVOKE OR
13 AMEND AN ANATOMICAL GIFT UPON THE DEATH OF THE DONOR;
14 TO REQUIRE CERTAIN REPORTING OF PROCUREMENT
15 ORGANIZATIONS; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
